OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy, some fog patches
OL,6,Fover Shetland, but with some sunny
OL,7,Fintervals breaking through. A few
OL,8,Flight showers, then some rain
OL,9,Fspreading north in the afternoon, with
OL,10,Fmoderate southeast breezes developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain continues to spread
OL,13,Fnorth over Shetland this evening,
OL,14,Fwhile Orkney turns generally dry.
OL,15,FBecoming rather murky through the
OL,16,Fnight as Haar become widespread,
OL,17,Fespecially for Shetland.
OL,18,
OL,19,CTuesday:FCloudy and dull with rather
OL,20,Fwidespread Haar. Risk of rain in the
OL,21,Fafternoon, mainly for Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
