OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,7,Fmix of bright spells and showers.
OL,8,FOften rather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
